features: 【Compatible with Ram ProMaster 1500 2500 3500 Light 】ZEBANERT H7 LED Bulbs Compatible with 2015-2021 RAM PROMASTER CITY,Compatible with 2019-2022 RAM 1500 2500 3500,Compatible with 2014-2020 Dodge Promaster 1500 2500 3500 van.As long as your factory lights are H7/H7LL, ZEBANERT led Bulbs directly fit and work.

【13000LM HIgh Brightness】EBANERT H7 LED bulb features new upgraded CSP 3570 LED chips, offering 55W 13000LM 6000K high brightness white light per set. 400% Brighter than the original/stock halogen,Emit bright and continuous light, high illumination clarity and visibility are brighter than the original, farewell to the dim narrow lighting range. The low beam High Beam mode is the same as the original halogen bulb.

【Plug and play】 H7 high beam or H7 low beam LED bulbs are design in completely 1:1 size, No bulky heatsank and external driver, No need to worry about the closing of the dust cover or the insufficient space, Easily achieve a 6 minutes fast installation without any modifications.

【50,000+ Hours Lifespan】ZEBANERT H7 bulbs body is made of aviation aluminum material, which has good heat dissipation performance and high corrosion resistance, reducing bulb replacement frequency. Fanless design allows heat to radiate silently,effectively extending the service life of more than 50,000 hours.

【3570 CSP Process Chip】H7 LED Light Bulbs use the latest 3570 CSP chip, 3570 CSP chip has higher light color accuracy and greater luminous Angle,so that the headlight irradiation range without black spots,more suitable for the use of automotive LED Light Bulbs.
